        <p>
            StreamSurfer ("us", "we", or "our") operates <a href="https://streamsurfer.info">https://streamsurfer.info</a> (the "Site"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the Site.
